#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.extra.ascend.libdevice.index_select_simd"
msgstr "# triton.language.extra.ascend.libdevice.index_select_simd"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:4
msgid "在非尾轴维度上并行 gather 多个索引，并以 tile 为单位将数据零拷贝地从全局内存（GM）直接搬运到统一缓冲区（UB）的正确位置。该操作等效于 `torch.index_select` 的高性能实现，适用于嵌入层查找、稀疏索引访问等场景。"
msgstr "Parallel gather multiple indices on non-tail axis dimensions, and directly copy data from global memory (GM) to the correct positions in the unified buffer (UB) in units of tiles with zero-copy. This operation is equivalent to a high-performance implementation of `torch.index_select`, suitable for scenarios such as embedding layer lookup and sparse index access."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:8
msgid "- `triton.language.extra.ascend.libdevice.index_select_simd(src, dim, index, src_shape, src_offset, read_shape)`"
msgstr "- `triton.language.extra.ascend.libdevice.index_select_simd(src, dim, index, src_shape, src_offset, read_shape)`"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Function:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:12
msgid ""
"- 在源张量的指定维度上，根据索引数组批量读取数据\n"
"- 支持指定读取区域的偏移和大小，实现灵活的切片\n"
"- 零拷贝高效实现，直接从 GM 搬运到 UB\n"
"- 保持元素类型和编码方式不变\n"
msgstr ""
"- On the specified dimension of the source tensor, batch read data according to the index array\n"
"- Support specifying the offset and size of the read region for flexible slicing\n"
"- Zero-copy efficient implementation, directly moving data from GM to UB\n"
"- Keep the element type and encoding unchanged\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:14
msgid "**典型应用场景：**"
msgstr "**Typical Application Scenarios:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:16
msgid ""
"- 嵌入层（Embedding）查找：从大词汇表中根据 token ID 批量读取词向量\n"
"- 稀疏张量操作：根据稀疏索引访问密集张量的特定行\n"
"- 动态路由和注意力机制：根据动态计算的索引选择特定特征\n"
msgstr ""
"- Embedding layer lookup: batch reading word vectors from a large vocabulary based on token IDs\n"
"- Sparse tensor operations: accessing specific rows of a dense tensor based on sparse indices\n"
"- Dynamic routing and attention mechanisms: selecting specific features based on dynamically computed indices\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:18
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:20
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:22
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| src | tensor/pointer | 是 | 源张量指针，位于全局内存（GM）上的数据 |\n"
"| dim | int | 是 | 在哪个维度执行 index_select 操作，取值范围 [0, len(src_shape)-2]，**不支持尾轴**（最后一个维度） |\n"
"| index | tensor | 是 | 1D 索引数组，位于 UB 上，指定要读取的索引位置 |\n"
"| src_shape | Tuple[int] | 是 | 源张量的完整形状 |\n"
"| src_offset | Tuple[int] | 是 | 从哪个位置开始读取，在 dim 维度可设为 -1（该维度由 index 决定） |\n"
"| read_shape | Tuple[int] | 是 | 读取数据的大小，在 dim 维度必须设为 -1（该维度由 index 长度决定） |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| src | tensor/pointer | Yes | Source tensor pointer, data located in global memory (GM) |\n"
"| dim | int | Yes | The dimension on which to perform the index_select operation, value range [0, len(src_shape)-2], **does not support the last axis** (the final dimension) |\n"
"| index | tensor | Yes | 1D index array, located in UB, specifying the index positions to read |\n"
"| src_shape | Tuple[int] | Yes | The full shape of the source tensor |\n"
"| src_offset | Tuple[int] | Yes | The starting position for reading; can be set to -1 on the dim dimension (this dimension is determined by index) |\n"
"| read_shape | Tuple[int] | Yes | The size of data to read; must be set to -1 on the dim dimension (this dimension is determined by the length of index) |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:24
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:26
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor (位于 UB 上)\n"
"- **形状：** 与 read_shape 一致，其中 dim 维度的大小等于 index 的长度\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与源张量相同\n"
"- **内存位置：** 统一缓冲区（UB）\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor (located on UB)\n"
"- **Shape:** consistent with read_shape, where the size of the dim dimension equals the length of index\n"
"- **Data type:** same as the source tensor\n"
"- **Memory location:** unified buffer (UB)\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:28
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:30
msgid ""
"- `read_shape[dim]` 必须为 -1\n"
"- `src_offset[dim]` 可以设为 -1（会被忽略，因为该维度由 index 决定）\n"
"- `len(src_shape) == len(src_offset) == len(read_shape)`\n"
"- `index` 必须是 1D 张量\n"
"- `dim` 不能是尾轴（最后一个维度），即 `dim < len(src_shape) - 1`\n"
"- 对于非 dim 维度：`0 <= src_offset[i] < src_shape[i]`\n"
"- 对于非 dim 维度：`src_offset[i] + read_shape[i] <= src_shape[i]`（超出边界自动截断）\n"
"- index 中的索引值必须在 `[0, src_shape[dim])` 范围内\n"
msgstr ""
"- `read_shape[dim]` must be -1  \n"
"- `src_offset[dim]` can be set to -1 (it will be ignored because this dimension is determined by `index`)  \n"
"- `len(src_shape) == len(src_offset) == len(read_shape)`  \n"
"- `index` must be a 1D tensor  \n"
"- `dim` cannot be the last axis (the trailing dimension), i.e., `dim < len(src_shape) - 1`  \n"
"- For non-dim dimensions: `0 <= src_offset[i] < src_shape[i]`  \n"
"- For non-dim dimensions: `src_offset[i] + read_shape[i] <= src_shape[i]` (out-of-bounds values are automatically truncated)  \n"
"- The index values in `index` must be within the range `[0, src_shape[dim])`\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:32
msgid "### 2.2 DataType支持表"
msgstr "### 2.2 DataType Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:34
msgid ""
"| 支持情况 | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|----------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU支持 | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Support Status | int8 | int16 | int32 | int64 | uint8 | uint16 | uint32 | uint64 | float16 | float32 | bfloat16 | float8e4 | float8e5 | float64 | bool |\n"
"|---------------|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:----:|:-----:|:-----:|:-----:|:------:|:------:|:-------:|:----:|:----:|:------:|:---:|\n"
"| Ascend A2/A3 | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | × | × | × | ✓ |\n"
"| GPU Support | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A | N/A |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:36
msgid "**说明：**"
msgstr "**Note:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:38
msgid ""
"- index 的数据类型必须为 int32 或 int64\n"
"- GPU 平台不支持此操作（Ascend 专用 intrinsic）\n"
msgstr ""
"- The data type of `index` must be `int32` or `int64`\n"
"- This operation is not supported on the GPU platform (Ascend-specific intrinsic)\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:40
msgid "### 2.3 Shape支持表"
msgstr "### 2.3 Shape Support Table"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:42
msgid "支持任意维度数（1D 到高维张量），但需满足以下条件："
msgstr "Supports any number of dimensions (from 1D to high-dimensional tensors), subject to the following conditions:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:44
msgid ""
"- index 必须是 1D 张量\n"
"- 源张量的各维度大小需根据实际硬件内存限制\n"
"- read_shape 在非 dim 维度上的大小需考虑 UB 空间限制\n"
msgstr ""
"- `index` must be a 1D tensor\n"
"- The size of each dimension of the source tensor must be determined based on actual hardware memory constraints\n"
"- The size of `read_shape` on non-`dim` dimensions must account for UB space limitations\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:46
msgid "**常见形状组合：**"
msgstr "**Common Shape Combinations:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:48
msgid ""
"- 2D 张量：适用于嵌入层查找、稀疏矩阵行选择\n"
"- 3D 张量：适用于批量嵌入查找、序列特征提取\n"
"- 高维张量：适用于复杂的多维索引操作\n"
msgstr ""
"- 2D tensor: suitable for embedding layer lookup, sparse matrix row selection\n"
"- 3D tensor: suitable for batch embedding lookup, sequence feature extraction\n"
"- High-dimensional tensor: suitable for complex multi-dimensional indexing operations\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:50
msgid "### 2.4 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.4 Special Limitations Explanation"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:52
msgid ""
"1. **dim 限制：** 不支持在尾轴（最后一个维度）上执行 index_select 操作，dim 必须满足 `dim < len(src_shape) - 1`\n"
"2. **数据类型限制：** 暂不支持 uint16/uint32/uint64/float8/float64 数据类型\n"
"3. **索引越界：** 不检查 index 中的索引是否越界，用户需自行保证索引合法性\n"
msgstr ""
"1. **dim Restriction:** The `index_select` operation is not supported on the trailing axis (the last dimension); `dim` must satisfy `dim < len(src_shape) - 1`.\n"
"2. **Data Type Restriction:** Data types uint16, uint32, uint64, float8, and float64 are currently not supported.\n"
"3. **Index Out of Bounds:** Whether the indices in `index` are out of bounds is not checked; users must ensure the validity of the indices themselves.\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:54
msgid "### 2.5 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.5 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:56
msgid "**基本用法（2D 嵌入查找）：**"
msgstr "**Basic Usage (2D Embedding Lookup):**"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:58
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"import triton\n"
"import triton.language as tl\n"
"import triton.language.extra.ascend.libdevice as libdevice\n"
"\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def embedding_kernel(\n"
"    embed_ptr,      # [vocab_size, embed_dim]\n"
"    indices_ptr,    # [batch_size]\n"
"    output_ptr,     # [batch_size, embed_dim]\n"
"    vocab_size: tl.constexpr,\n"
"    embed_dim: tl.constexpr,\n"
"):\n"
"    pid = tl.program_id(0)\n"
"\n"
"    # 加载索引\n"
"    indices = tl.load(indices_ptr + pid * 16 + tl.arange(0, 16))\n"
"\n"
"    # 使用 index_select 批量读取嵌入向量\n"
"    embeddings = libdevice.index_select_simd(\n"
"        src=embed_ptr,\n"
"        dim=0,\n"
"        index=indices,\n"
"        src_shape=(vocab_size, embed_dim),\n"
"        src_offset=(-1, 0),\n"
"        read_shape=(-1, embed_dim)\n"
"    )\n"
"\n"
"    # 存储结果\n"
"    offsets = tl.arange(0, 16)[:, None] * embed_dim + tl.arange(0, embed_dim)[None, :]\n"
"    tl.store(output_ptr + pid * 16 * embed_dim + offsets, embeddings)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:60
msgid "**与 torch.index_select 的关系：**"
msgstr "**Relationship with torch.index_select:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:62
msgid ""
"- `index_select_simd` 等价于 `torch.index_select(src, dim, index)` 加上切片操作\n"
"- 但 index_select_simd 在硬件层面实现，性能优于 PyTorch 实现（约 0.6~1.5x AscendC 性能）\n"
msgstr ""
"- `index_select_simd` is equivalent to `torch.index_select(src, dim, index)` combined with a slicing operation\n"
"- However, `index_select_simd` is implemented at the hardware level, offering better performance than the PyTorch implementation (approximately 0.6~1.5x AscendC performance)\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:64
msgid "**与常规 load 的差异：**"
msgstr "**Differences from regular load:**"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Extension_Ops/index_select_simd.md:66
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"## 常规 load 方式（低效）\n"
"for i in range(len(indices)):\n"
"    idx = tl.load(indices_ptr + i)\n"
"    offsets = idx * stride + tl.arange(0, size)\n"
"    data = tl.load(src_ptr + offsets)\n"
"    # ... 处理 data\n"
"\n"
"## index_select 方式（高效）\n"
"indices = tl.load(indices_ptr + tl.arange(0, len(indices)))\n"
"data = libdevice.index_select_simd(\n"
"    src=src_ptr,\n"
"    dim=0,\n"
"    index=indices,\n"
"    src_shape=(...),\n"
"    src_offset=(-1, 0),\n"
"    read_shape=(-1, size)\n"
")\n"
"## 一次性获取所有数据\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

